Pour juice into medium microwaveable bowl, sprinkle gelatin over juice. Let stand 5 minutes to dissolve. Heat juice and gelatin in microwave on High for 15 seconds, stir, repeat. Pour juice mixture into blender, add fruit, yogurt, and liquid gelatin. Puree for 3 minutes until smooth. Pour into pie shell and refrigerate 4 hours. Garnish with whipped cream and strawberries.